    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Solid good-condition example that appears complete, presentable, and ready to enjoy as a driver. It shows well overall with decent paint, trim, and interior, and it comes across as a car that has been cared for, though it still has the normal light cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections you\u2019d expect from a used vehicle. This is not a perfect show car, but it is an honest, well-sorted car that should make a satisfying driver for someone who wants something attractive and usable.",
