      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "A practical, affordable vehicle for buyers who want dependable basic transportation without overspending. This car shows its age, but it offers solid value as a budget-friendly daily driver, backup vehicle, or starter car. Priced to sell and presented with honest appeal for someone who recognizes a worthwhile low-cost opportunity.",
