    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s perfect for someone after cheap wheels, a tidy project, or a handy backup runabout. It\u2019s being sold in poor condition, so please don\u2019t expect a showroom car \u2014 but if you\u2019re practical and know how to get the most out of a used vehicle, there\u2019s value here. A straightforward, affordable option with plenty of potential for the right buyer. Priced to sell and happy to answer questions.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with strong bones and plenty of usable life left. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the transmission engages as it should, and it offers the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes ownership approachable for a hands-on buyer. Cosmetically it shows its age and it\u2019s not a showpiece, but for someone looking for affordable transportation, a weekend project, or a platform to sort and improve, this one makes a compelling case. Priced to move and well suited to a buyer who values function, serviceability, and potential over perfection.",
      "price": 4950.0,
